{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Animation.currentTime","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation\"><code>Animation()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><em><code>currentTime</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect\"><code>effect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\"><code>finished</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/id\"><code>id</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pending\"><code>pending</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate\"><code>playbackRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>playState</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready\"><code>ready</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/replaceState\"><code>replaceState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\"><code>startTime</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/timeline\"><code>timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>cancel()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/commitStyles\"><code>commitStyles()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>finish()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>pause()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/persist\"><code>persist()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>play()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>reverse()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/updatePlaybackRate\"><code>updatePlaybackRate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>cancel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event\"><code>finish</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/remove_event\"><code>remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Animations</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationPlaybackEvent\"><code>AnimationPlaybackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getAnimations\"><code>Document.getAnimations()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta é uma <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tecnologia experimental (en-US)</a></strong><br>Verifique a <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">tabela de compatibilidade entre Navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usar essa funcionalidade em produção.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>A propriedade&nbsp;<code><strong>Animation</strong></code><strong><code>.currentTime</code></strong>&nbsp;da&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a>&nbsp;retorna e altera&nbsp;o tempo atual da animação em milésimos de segundos, seja estando em execução ou pausada.</p>\n\n<p>Se a animação não tem uma <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, está inativa, ou ainda não foi colocada em execução, o valor de retorno do&nbsp;<code>currentTime </code>será<code> null</code>.&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var<em>tempoAtual</em> = <em>Animation</em>.currentTime;\n<em>Animation</em>.currentTime =<em> novoTempo;</em></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor","title":"Valor","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Um número que representará no tempo atual da animação em milésimos de segundos, ou&nbsp;<code>null</code> para desativar a animação.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>No <a href=\"https://codepen.io/rachelnabors/pen/PNYGZQ?editors=0010\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">jogo Drink Me/Eat Me</a>, O tamanho da Alice&nbsp;é animado e pode crescer ou&nbsp;diminuir. No início do jogo, o tamanho dela foi colocado entre os dois extremos do animation's <code>currentTime</code>&nbsp;no meio do&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code>'s duration</a>, desta maneira:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>aliceChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>currentTime <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> aliceChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>effect<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>timing<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>duration <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Outra forma mais genérica para encontrar o marco de 50% da animação pode ser feito da seguinte forma:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>currentTime <span class=\"token operator\">=</span>\n  animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>effect<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getComputedTiming</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>delay <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>\n  animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>effect<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getComputedTiming</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>activeDuration <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificações</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#dom-animation-currenttime\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Animations<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'currentTime' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Rascunho atual</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>39.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/48\" title=\"Released on 2016-08-02.\">48</a> (48)<sup>[1]</sup></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Phone</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>39.0</td>\n   <td>48.0 (48)<sup>[1]</sup></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>39.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] A&nbsp;Web Animations API está ativa por padrão apenas no Firefox Developer Edition e nas versões do&nbsp;Nightly. Você pode habilitá-la em versões&nbsp;beta configurando a preferência <code>dom.animations-api.core.enabled</code>&nbsp;para&nbsp;<code>true</code>, e também desativar em qualquer&nbsp;Firefox mudando esta mesma preferência para&nbsp;<code>false</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a> para outros métodos e propriedades que você pode usar para controlar a animação da página web.</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\"><code>Animation.startTime</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> para o tempo que a animação está programada começar.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"A propriedade Animation.currentTime da Web Animations API retorna e altera o tempo atual da animação em milésimos de segundos, seja estando em execução ou pausada.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation.currentTime","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Animation.currentTime","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Animation.currentTime","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/animation/currenttime","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/animation/currenttime/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime","title":"Animation.currentTime"}],"pageTitle":"Animation.currentTime - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}